{"tid":2392986,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"華為擺脫不了 Google！「鴻蒙」遭爆裡子仍是 Android 沒創新","createTime":"2021-02-03T07:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T01:28:53.000Z","uid":221827,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cc00417f05fd62d33d85b4be3b5ecf260ba660a6","tid":2392986,"uid":221827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"為了因應美國制裁，華為自行研發鴻蒙（Harmony）OS 系統企圖取代 Android，儘管軟體部門總裁王成錄曾對外喊話，表示鴻蒙不是 Android、iOS 的複製品。外媒深入研究卻發現，整套系統根本還是 Android。<br />\n<br />\n外媒《Ars Technica》實際申請鴻蒙的開發者版本，與 Android、iOS 的申請流程不同，華為竟然要求提交護照、身分證、信用卡等詳細資訊，有嚴格的實名制驗證，頗具「中國風格」。官方也不允許下載整套作業系統，會以類似雲端模擬器的方式，提供開發者測試。<br />\n<br />\n完成申請後，下載可以識別系統的 App，儘管系統強調是鴻蒙，多半軟體卻仍會顯示 Android，更能看系統內包含多個帶有 Android 命名的檔案。外媒測試任何，鴻蒙沒有開發出真正的新功能與區別，幾乎與 Android 10 版本沒有任何差異。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，鴻蒙嚴格說起來更像是亞馬遜的 FireOS，兩者都只能算是 Android 的分支系統，華為僅是將所有 Android 字眼替換成「Harmony」，與三星曾經想推出的 Tizen 和 Google Fuchsia 相比，鴻蒙根本算不上「全新」系統，大致上仍是一款魔改的開源版本 Android。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/43169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F43169&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrSDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=d54693b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F43169&h=536915f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/43169</a>"},{"pid":"99538783be4d8a53c259db9a16acd9932dcc6500","tid":2392986,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T07:03:58.000Z","msg":"到佢真係自煮研發先出新聞啦"},{"pid":"c29d53563d21507b89f2b2b193c289ff1cb0f2f3","tid":2392986,"uid":165136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"過一陣就話你Android open source 預咗可以比人改㗎啦"},{"pid":"635d5a8e5824cebe3af5cb300db45e72429d5524","tid":2392986,"uid":274278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"0%抄襲才是新聞"},{"pid":"afb12d07400f3c80e58efe7a44b00a1e004f30a6","tid":2392986,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T07:18:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"825b4c4374a0ee62da5e44bbfe2ab9728f9bf7c8","tid":2392986,"uid":55873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T07:26:48.000Z","msg":"究竟同一單鴻懵 可以分開幾多階段慢慢鞭c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91057f513fe932ce5528705d178ace83c33284b3","tid":2392986,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T07:28:50.000Z","msg":"制裁個記者啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ac10890dda94e58621ca089681739c35315e37","tid":2392986,"uid":189638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T07:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />華為請唔請人<br />\n<br />\n我識copy and paste完仲識改logo。咁撚勁嘅人才去邊度搵。"},{"pid":"fe429d0905ff942a7216ccae87e705fe0e0d24e2","tid":2392986,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T01:28:53.000Z","msg":"又係紅芯啲frd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}